# рҹҺҷпёҸ Voice AI вҖ“ Multi-Agent Conversational Assistant

An AI-powered real-time voice assistant built using **LiveKit**, **LangGraph**, **RAG**, **ChromaDB**, and **Groq LLM**.

The assistant understands spoken language, retrieves information from a knowledge base, routes requests to specialized AI agents, and responds naturally using speech synthesis.

---

## рҹҡҖ Features

- рҹҺӨ Real-time Speech-to-Text
- рҹ§  Multi-Agent Architecture
- рҹ“ҡ Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- рҹ”Һ Semantic Search with ChromaDB
- рҹӨ– LangGraph-based Agent Routing
- вҡЎ Groq LLM Integration
- рҹ”Ҡ Text-to-Speech Responses
- вҳҒпёҸ Deployable on Railway
- рҹҢҗ LiveKit Voice Pipeline

---

