---

## вҡҷпёҸ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Bheeshma21/Voice-AI.git

cd Voice-AI

python -m venv .venv

source .venv/bin/activate
```

Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## рҹ”‘ Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file

```
LIVEKIT_URL=

LIVEKIT_API_KEY=

LIVEKIT_API_SECRET=

DEEPGRAM_API_KEY=

GROQ_API_KEY=

CARTESIA_API_KEY=
```

---

## рҹ“ҡ Create Vector Database

```bash
python rag/ingest.py
```

---

## в–¶пёҸ Run

```bash
python app.py start
```

For development

```bash
python app.py dev
```

